Install libpnicore python bindings
==================================

Description
===========
This package provides some functionality from the pnicore C++ library. 
It hardly exports any user functionality but is quite useful for extension 
developers as it provides some functionality that makes life easier. 

Installation
============
To install the package the following libraries must be installed

.) libpnicore including all its dependencies
.) boost_python 
.) python including developer packages (header files and libraries)
.) numpy including its header files

The installation runs via distutils using the well known

$>python setup.py install

along with all its options.
